HEADWORD: Florida bean
<hw>Flor"i*da bean"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>The large, roundish, flattened seed of <spn>Mucuna urens</spn>. See
under <er>Bean</er>.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>One of the very large seeds
of the <spn>Entada scandens</spn>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Florideae</ent>⟦br⟧
